          A comprehensive 25-point checklist to identify gaps, improve security, and optimize your technology infrastructure
        </p>
        <div class="checklist-meta">
          <span class="meta-item">âœ“ Free Download</span>
          <span class="meta-item">âœ“ Print-Friendly</span>
          <span class="meta-item">âœ“ Used by 500+ Businesses</span>
        </div>
      </div>

