                <strong>Firewall is configured and regularly updated</strong>
                <small>Next-gen firewall with IDS/IPS, ruleset reviewed quarterly</small>
              </span>
            </label>
            <label class="checklist-item">
              <input type="checkbox" />
              <span class="item-text">
                <strong>Multi-factor authentication (MFA) is enforced</strong>
                <small>MFA required for all critical systems and remote access</small>
              </span>
            </label>
            <label class="checklist-item">
